[02:49:40.662] [INFO ]     Of course. Here is a detailed comparison of the NovaLens Professional and Business pricing tiers.
    
    The primary difference between these tiers is the **scale of usage and the level of administrative control**. Professional is designed for individual power users or small teams, while Business is built for organization-wide deployment with centralized management.
    
    Here is a side-by-side comparison:
    
    | Feature | NovaLens Professional | NovaLens Business |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | **Target User** | Individual professionals, freelancers, small teams. | Medium to large organizations, departments. |
    | **Pricing Model** | **Per-user, per-month** subscription. | **Volume-based, annual** contract. Pricing is customized based on the number of seats and required features. |
    | **Core AI Features** | ✅ Full access to all Nova AI models (including latest releases).<br>✅ Advanced data analysis & file upload.<br>✅ High usage limits (e.g., 10,000 queries/month). | ✅ Full access to all Nova AI models.<br>✅ Advanced data analysis & file upload.<br>✅ Significantly higher or custom usage limits. |
    | **Administrative Controls** | Basic user management for a small team. | ✅ **Centralized User Management:** Provision/de-provision users via SCIM (e.g., with Okta, Azure AD).<br>✅ **Usage Analytics Dashboard:** Monitor aggregate and per-user usage.<br>✅ **Custom Policy Enforcement:** Set guidelines for AI use. |
    | **Security & Compliance** | Standard security protocols. | ✅ **Enhanced Security:** SSO/SAML authentication, private deployment options.<br>✅ **Data Governance:** API access for data retention policies, audit logs.<br>✅ **Priority Support & SLAs:** Guaranteed uptime and dedicated support channels. |
    | **API Access** | Limited API credits included. | ✅ **High-Priority API Access:** Dedicated throughput, higher rate limits.<br>✅ **Custom Integrations:** Support for building Nova AI into internal applications. |
    | **Support** | Standard email support. | ✅ **Account Manager:** Dedicated point of contact.<br>✅ **Priority 24/7 Technical Support.** |
    
    ### Key Takeaways:
    
    *   **Choose Professional if:** You are an individual or a small team that needs powerful AI capabilities without the need for complex user management or enterprise-level security. It's a straightforward, per-user subscription.
    *   **Choose Business if:** You are an organization that needs to deploy NovaLens to many users, require centralized control and billing, need to enforce security policies (like SSO), and want dedicated support and custom terms. The pricing is not publicly listed because it is negotiated annually based on your company's specific needs.
    
    For the most accurate and current pricing, you should always check the official NovaAI pricing page or contact the sales team directly for a Business quote.
