    ### NovaLens Professional vs. Business: Pricing Comparison
    
    | Feature | NovaLens Professional | NovaLens Business |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | **Target User** | Individual professionals, freelancers, small teams | Medium to large businesses, departments |
    | **Pricing Model** | Per-user, monthly subscription | Per-user, monthly or annual subscription |
