    | **Price (Annual)** | **$44.10 per user / month** (billed as $529.20 annually, saving 10%) | **$89.10 per user / month** (billed as $1,069.20 annually, saving 10%) |
    | **Core Features** | All NovaLens Standard features, plus: <br> • Advanced AI model access (GPT-4, Claude 3 Opus)<br> • 5,000 AI credits/month<br> • Customizable AI workflows<br> • Priority email support | All NovaLens Professional features, plus: <br> • Unlimited AI credits<br> • Advanced team management & admin controls<br> • Single Sign-On (SSO) <br> • API access for integration<br> • Dedicated account manager & phone support |
    
    ### Key Differentiators
    
